Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下次 去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得波浪的声音有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}晚上没回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前也有过喜欢的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只觉得不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而没有其他的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}连我自己也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}竟然喜欢上了那么天然的女孩子 真让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真希望你不再需要我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…不讨厌你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我听到的 全是你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看到的 也全是驱同学的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 现在游什么项目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}50米自由泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前些日子我突破32秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}争取到秋天能达到31秒00
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}阳菜 真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳姐姐 也一直朝着做模特的梦想努力着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我会默默地为你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身材果然不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下次跟我一起去买衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我帮你挑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 真的吗 我一定去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 抱歉 没打招呼就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们去外面说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 阳菜 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天小雪的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳的那记耳光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是没办法的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也觉得驱同学做得过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子太容易让人看懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我很容易懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪 真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那家伙 难道不知道自己毫无胜算的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸今天要住院了 你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 说是住院检查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样的话 就不用那么担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们得少去探望她 尽量别去打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 不能去打扰恋人的相会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸果然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像挺顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想我们去看她的话 她一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}最近大家都不怎么聚得起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自从那个大卫来了 总感觉很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可乐 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}医院的探病时间结束得超级早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}晚上十点前不知道能做到些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}钢琴家的握力真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}接下来渐强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fsp0\fs34.5\pos(1047,985.5)}crescendo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}极强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fsp0\fs34.5\pos(960,985.5)}fortissimo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 妈妈也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要有什么需要的话和我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是你朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我男朋友 祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是幸的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…我是小幸的男…男朋友 白崎祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是爷爷做的曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这里竟然有燕子的巢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 有雏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像是呢 能确认两只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明明我是一直在这儿住着的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学却比我了解得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道点儿这城市的些碎小事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和透子生活过的日久天长比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学 很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 好像让你看到了丢人的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天小柳来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说起了昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是好朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我和驱同学 是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 一下子不敢看驱同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们已经超越…因为眼中的未来而同病相怜…的关系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}刚才看到驱同学掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}未来是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还是要去海边 那里比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天去海边 一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来了 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也准时登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来了 五点半的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那位…是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你认得他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和他说过话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}从没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之超帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是关系好像变得很麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}井美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}教练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你一直在坚持练习的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看了你之前纪录赛的成绩 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没这事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有什么想说的就来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 后天开始有一周的夏季合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}最好在那之前或之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大早上的真有精神呢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}阳菜也每天都在积极参加社团活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天我看到雪哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}从我们泳池可以看到他每天定时跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后 虽然有些不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉渐渐成为我们部的偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她们吵着要建粉丝应援团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不愧是小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这个世界真小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为小雪很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有人气是当然的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}确实 他跑起来的样子很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错 小雪很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 你还真不会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 我去探望小幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我也该走了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 现在马上要开始检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 我差不多也该回了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}每天都来 多谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么样 身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}让我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}祐送来的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那位冲仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后呢 驱同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说了一些过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}听了这些的小柳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗 听说明天天气也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}两个人一起看海就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就会？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就会看到一些新东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是那些一闪一闪的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和驱同学在一起 我觉得自己渐渐知道那是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等再弄清楚一些了 我就向小幸报告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老师马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久违了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是深水透子的妹妹 深水阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 那个 请不要这么逊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 请不要这么逊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不是未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了 小幸 这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想看海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天我就出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下午大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想见见雪哉和小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到晚上我还想放烟花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}事出突然 透子就由我来联系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去告诉柳和雪哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天发短信说的去海边那事你还没回我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过应该能去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳倒是回我说能去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天是和女朋友去海边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}把他养成了个奇怪的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 我倒觉得是个很有魅力的男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这可真不像一个母亲说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前那事 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以 检查要拖一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天才可以出院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸 我昨天也应该和你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}给男朋友添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 哪有什么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}男朋友什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 总之先发短信通知今天的活动终止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 讨厌大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个人在 大家就零零散散的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 确实 最近大家很难聚在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了 你怎么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}改到明天去海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天透子在日乃出海滩和大卫约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以一开始我就没联系透子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 这不就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为自己讨厌大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以想要大家一起赶去干扰透子的约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是想让我联系大家这么做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 这不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 今天先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}祐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs60\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&\frz32\fax0.1\pos(508,709)}抱歉 今天去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说是今天不去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天不去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 我不讨厌等人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还是久等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}波浪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和以前的感觉有点儿不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也许这还是第一次在这种时候来海边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这个 送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}蜻蜓玻璃球？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:40.29,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an7\fs48}在彩色玻璃表面上镶嵌不同颜色玻璃的玻璃球。似蜻蜓的眼睛，故名。\N约公元前1500年出现于埃及、美索不达米亚。后从东方各地经中国传入日本。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一对儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子说过的「掉下去的我」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你绝对不能去高的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你觉得那真的可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}夸张点儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我今后一辈子都不能去有一点儿可能会掉下来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那些真的是「未来的碎片」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是驱同学告诉我那是未来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再仔细想想比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去买果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱同学要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我要水就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我小时候真不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么大人要专门拿钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去自贩机买水买茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明明有哈尔必思水什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你也被叫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子没和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她去买饮料了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 趁这个机会我就先说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪变成这副样子都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打扰你们了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是般配的一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你好好给我说明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不问了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你放了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有点想见乔纳森了
